{"tid":716734,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西一酒吧：尼馬每在比賽中倒地一次，全場送一杯酒","createTime":"2018-06-25T13:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T15:27:09.000Z","uid":8985,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f7aab78a99c2583d5b50926c52a50bb497118545","tid":716734,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:42:18.000Z","msg":"《阿斯報》報導，巴西里約熱內盧一家名叫 Sir Walter Pub 的酒吧想出一項宣傳活動。巴西頭牌尼馬每在比賽中倒地一次，就送一杯酒。被當地人得知後，這家酒吧的預約電話就被打爆。<br />\n<br />\n本屆世界杯上，尼馬在兩場比賽中已被侵犯14次，其中10次來自對陣瑞士的比賽。這一數據是英格蘭傳奇前鋒阿蘭-希勒在1998年對陣突尼西亞的比賽中被侵犯11次後最多的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/214133_917e54d351c67a03ffbaa10df7cacca1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F214133_917e54d351c67a03ffbaa10df7cacca1.png&h=f865e89e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17093eae024eda3cdeeda64037801f75123ec268","tid":716734,"uid":8985,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baac748e40e236eff9c45ab18e36c76c7095b531","tid":716734,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇執笠"},{"pid":"f3fafd0d87fb86664cae50636ab54275ad9f7707","tid":716734,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://7xthnd.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/home4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F7xthnd.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com%2Fhome4.jpg&h=d0d80a01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c0ba5bcf566f452c0710b6e06af68b80a19a577","tid":716734,"uid":67028,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁唔洗嗌酒啦 剩係送既都夠醉"},{"pid":"6c0bc05a02111b4463d77e3f47d47c1083d52b1e","tid":71673